<P>A LECTURE ON THE PERPETUAL MOTION.</P>
<Q>Haud facil&egrave; inventum perpetuum-mobile purum artificiale; haudquaquam quod fieri non pote&s;t:
<BIBL>BERNOULLI.</BIBL></Q>
